name: Unleashing the Power of Generative AI and Intelligent Agents: Transforming the Future
description: Participants get the opportunity to unlock the transformative potential of Generative AI and intelligent agents in our immersive workshop. This hands-on experience brings together cutting-edge AI technologies—ChatGPT (GPT-3), Synthesia, StyleGAN, and DALL-E 2. Explore the power of artificial intelligence in shaping the future, as we dive into the realms of natural language processing, code generation, and real-time applications.
speaker: Prabakaran Chandran, Senior Machine Learning Engineer at Informatica Bengaluru.
speaker_detail: Prabakaran Chandran is a Senior Machine Learning Engineer at Informatica Bengaluru. He is an experienced Mentor and Technical Speaker in the field of Machine Learning and Python. He has also worked as a Data Scientist and Apprentice Leader at Mu Sigma Inc. Bengaluru.

name: Multi modal AI System for Autonomous diagnosis
description: Unlock the transformative potential of Multi-modal AI Systems in the context of Autonomous Diagnosis in this immersive workshop. This hands-on experience delves into how AI is revolutionizing healthcare and diagnostic processes by combining various types of data—such as images, text, and sensor data—to drive intelligent and autonomous decision-making. Participants will explore cutting-edge technologies that are shaping the future of autonomous diagnosis, with practical applications in medical fields.
speaker: Prabakaran Chandran, Senior Machine Learning Engineer at Informatica Bengaluru
speaker_detail: Prabakaran Chandran, Senior Machine Learning Engineer at Informatica Bengaluru, is a seasoned expert in the fields of Machine Learning and AI. With experience as a mentor, speaker, and data science, he provides valuable insights into the deployment and future of multi-modal AI in healthcare.

name: Infrastructure Developments in Coimbatore
description: Discover the evolving landscape of Infrastructure Developments in Coimbatore in this immersive workshop. This hands-on experience focuses on the latest advancements in urban infrastructure, smart city initiatives, and industrial growth within Coimbatore, one of India’s most dynamic cities. Participants will explore the key drivers behind the city's growth, including transportation, sustainability, and technology integration, and gain insight into how infrastructure is shaping the city's future.
